/*
 ValveFlowController.ino
 ESP32 controls a relay-driven motorized valve on a schedule (08:00 open, 08:02 close)
 and monitors a water flow sensor (pulse output) to report whether water is flowing.

 - Uses <time.h> + configTime() for NTP time sync and POSIX TZ support.
 - Blynk IoT integration for remote monitoring and control.
 - Edit WiFi, TZ, Blynk auth and pins in the CONFIG section.
*/

